  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 20\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0d9a\u0da7\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "20 crore gold biscuits seized in Katunayake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An air passenger and an employee of the airport duty free shopping mall who tried to take out of the Katunayake airport a consignment of gold biscuits weighing 0.9 kg and 500 grams worth 205 million rupees (205 million rupees) were arrested by customs at the airport arrivals terminal. A group of officers of the drug control department have arrested them today (17th).",
        "He is a 39-year-old airline passenger residing in Nittambuwa area. He had arrived at Katunayake Airport today (17th) at 08.35 in the morning from Dubai by Emirates Airlines flight EK-650.",
        "Also, a 38-year-old woman from Seeduwa who worked at the Katunayake airport duty-free shopping complex.",
        "This air passenger has been arrested by the officers of the Customs Narcotics Control Division while attempting to leave the Katunayake airport with 80 gold biscuits weighing 116.6 grams in his luggage and this airport maid in her hand bag.",
        "At present, the airport customs officers are conducting further investigation on this matter while keeping the two in custody."
      ],
